                <mxCell id="19" value="&lt;div&gt;Noise example:&lt;/div&gt;[&#39;On 3 November 2022, a spokesman for the Federal Foreign Office (04.11.) issued the following statement on the consultations of the Foreign and Defence Ministers of Germany and Japan:&#39;, &#39;Foreign Minister Baerbock met Japanese Foreign Minister Hayashi in Münster on 3 November 2022 and conducted security policy consultations in 2+2 format together with Defence Minister Lambrecht and Japanese Defence Minister Hamada, both of whom had virtually joined forces.&#39;, &#39;In the spirit of the close and trustful partnership of values between Germany and Japan, ministers discussed current international issues, including the brutal Russian war of aggression against Ukraine, the situation in the Indo-Pacific and the Korean Peninsula, and the role of China.&#39;, &#39;They also exchanged views on bilateral issues such as work on the respective national security strategies and intensified armaments and defence cooperation.&#39;]" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
